  <summary date="2018-01-17T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Securing Our Schools Act of 2018

This bill establishes a pilot program under which the Department of Justice may award one-year grants to local education agencies for the purpose of purchasing and installing devices that allow for the immediate notification of appropriate officials in case of emergency.</summary>
